# Project: OpenImjang
Stack: React+Vite+TS (SPA), BFF(Hono/Fastify on Bun), PostGIS(SRID 4326)

Do:
- Frontend uses Kakao Maps JS SDK; never expose server keys.
- Use React Query for data fetching; hooks return {data,isLoading,error}.
- BFF routes: 
  GET /point-info?lon&lat  // PostGIS ST_Contains for zoning/parcel
  GET /risk-score?pnu      // combine landprice+deals to score
  GET /nearby?lon&lat&r    // POI/역/정류장 (proxy if needed)
- PostGIS: create GIST index on geom; return GeoJSON via ST_AsGeoJSON.
- Code style: ESLint+Prettier, TS strict, ESM modules.
- Cache external API responses 5–30m; limit bbox/radius and page size.
- Secrets live only in .env (server). Client uses VITE_* env only.

Don't:
- Call server-only APIs directly from the browser.
- Commit .env, large GeoJSON/CSV/MBTiles.
- Block the UI on long WFS calls; use BFF + caching.